Docs.summary: Result object given a corresponding GetValueRequest.

remarks.para:
Result object given a corresponding GetValueRequest.
  • If the request was successful, #getResultCode will be #RESULT_OK, #getValue will be populated with the settings preference value and #getMetadata will be populated with its metadata.
  • If the request is unsuccessful, #getResultCode be a value other than #RESULT_OK - see documentation for those possibilities to understand the cause of the failure.
